Aaron is a dedicated professional with a strong educational background in public administration and international relations. He holds a bachelor's degree in public administration and a master's degree in international relations, equipping him with a comprehensive understanding of governance, policymaking, and global affairs.

In addition to his formal education, Aaron has enhanced his skill set through two professional courses: one in Customer Experience Management with the Chartered Institute of Customer Management (CICM) and another in Virtual Assistance with Smart PA. These courses have provided him with practical skills in enhancing customer satisfaction and efficient administrative support.

With a passion for fostering positive customer experiences and a keen eye for detail, Aaron is committed to leveraging his expertise to drive organizational success and improve stakeholder engagement. His diverse background and focus on continuous learning make him a valuable asset in any professional setting.
